high_descs: Turn around 180 degrees and walk to the white table to your left, which is also left of a black appliance.  Stand in front of the white table.
Pick up the metal skillet that is on the table on the left of the sponge.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Open the bottom door of the fridge and put the skillet on the top shelf on the right hand side.
Pick up the apple that is on the bottom shelf of the fridge.
Place the apple in the metal skillet on the top shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put an apple into a metal skillet in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the table on your left.
Pick up the pan on the table.
Bring the pan to the fridge on the right.
Put pan in the fridge.
Pick up the apple in the fridge.
Put the apple in the pan in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Pan an apple in a pan in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and begin walking, then hang a left and walk up to the white table.
Pick up the large metal pot on the left end of the white table.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge, turn to face it.
Open the fridge door and place the metal pot on the top shelf of the lower compartment.
Pick up the tomato from the bottom shelf in the fridge.
Place the tomato into the large metal pot on the top shelf of the lower compartment of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a tomato in a large metal pot in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, move forward, then turn left to face the table.
Pick up the pot on the table.
Turn right, go forward, then turn left go to the fridge.
Put the pot in the fridge, on the top shelf and to the right.
Pick up the apple on the bottom shelf of the fridge.
Put the apple in the pot on the top shelf of the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put a pot in the fridge with an apple in it.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the corner of the white table.
Pick the silver bowl up from the table.
Walk the bowl over to the white fridge.
Place the bowl in the refrigerator.
Remove an apple from the fridge.
Place the apple in the silver bowl in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put an apple in a bowl in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and the go to the white table and turn to face it near the pan.
Pick the pan up from the white table.
Go to the right and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the bowl on the top shelf of the fridge.
Pick the apple up out of the fridge.
Put the apple in the bowl.
anns.task_desc: Put an apple in a bowl in the fridge.
